    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating recently applied, ensuring zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, and the original factory floor mats remain untouched. Mechanically, the car is flawless, benefiting from a fully documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Accompanied by all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning driver to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
